[https://f1000research.com/collections/BOSC?&selectedDomain=articles In 2018, BOSC was held jointly with GCC] as a combined [https://gccbosc2018.sched.com/ GCCBOSC] conference. We hope to partner with GCC again in 2020 or 2021. Read more [https://news.open-bio.org/2018/08/02/taking-turns/ here about why we decided to hold BOSC with GCC in 2018 and ISMB in 2019.]

If you are interested in giving a talk at BOSC 2019, [https://www.open-bio.org/wiki/BOSC_Abstract_Submission submit your abstract] by April 11!

